{"data":[{"date":"09:57 17/07","title":"Real Madrid c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/real-madrid-co-cau-tra-loi-ve-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gareth Bale r\u1eddi Real Madrid gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 sau cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai, t\u1edd The Telegraph tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Los Blancos.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Gareth Bale</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Zidane c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn \u1edf Champions League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Gareth Bale r\u1eddi Real Madrid  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Gareth Bale r\u1eddi Real Madrid  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/HLV-Lopetegui-quyet-khong-de-Gareth-Bale-roi-Real-Madrid--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Gareth Bale&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu n\u1ebfu t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. Vi\u1ec7c Bale tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real gi\u00fap nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t m\u1eebng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Gareth Bale, Mourinho \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i MU th\u00ec Tottenham v\u00e0 Bayern Munich c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u01b0a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Bale r\u1eddi Real l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gareth Bale r\u1eddi Real Madrid gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 sau cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai, t\u1edd The Telegraph tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Los Blancos.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"guong mat phan cam Gareth Bale\" title=\"guong mat phan cam Gareth Bale\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/real-madrid-co-cau-tra-loi-ve-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Gareth Bale \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real sau cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Lopetegui</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00f4m qua, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chot-thoi-diem-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale-180-191238.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bale c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Lopetegui</span>, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed5 l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Lopetegui sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Bale, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Real v\u1eeba m\u1ea5t Ronaldo v\u00e0o tay Juventus, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao n\u1eefa tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSong song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, HLV Lopetegui c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Eden Hazard \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real, Los Blancos c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1345","checkdouble":"191416"},{"date":"10:19 17/07","title":"HLV Sarri n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/hlv-sarri-noi-gi-ve-tan-binh-tri-gia-50-trieu-bang-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jorginho, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Jorginho</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay th\u1ebf Conte d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea, nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n mang v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Napoli t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jorginho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jorginho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/Maurizio-Sarri-phat-bieu-ve-Jorginho-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Jorginho</span>. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London, \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Napoli nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge ph\u1ea3i chi ra 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Chelsea, Jorginho s\u1ebd \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 5. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft, Jorginho chia s\u1ebb: \u201cChelsea l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf Anh m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u n\u1eefa, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i lu\u00f4n m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Premier League, b\u1edfi v\u1eady khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Chelsea t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng Chelsea c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u, hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c t\u1ed1t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Jorginho</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jorginho, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri giup Chelsea mua Jorginho\" title=\"Sarri gi\u00fap Chelsea mua Jorginho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/hlv-sarri-noi-gi-ve-tan-binh-tri-gia-50-trieu-bang-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Jorginho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cJorginho kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf Napoli, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi Jorginho, b\u00f3ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n li\u00ean t\u1ee5c, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea, t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ri\u00eang\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft t\u00f4i s\u1ebd n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n hi\u1ec3u h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n g\u00ec v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n g\u00ec. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecd h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho CLB\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1344","checkdouble":"191417"},{"date":"10:49 17/07","title":"Chelsea chi 115 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/chelsea-chi-115-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, HLV Mourinho \u0111ang thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c BL\u0110 M.U h\u1ecfi mua 2 ng\u00f4i sao Croatia c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U chi g\u1ea7n 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Ivan Perisic, c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u1ecd t\u1eebng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Inter \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, khi anh g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3, ng\u00f4i sao Croatia c\u0169ng ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Anh trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. T\u1eeb l\u00e2u, Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 48 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Perisic v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, v\u00e0 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Man United.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp theo, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng \u0111ang theo s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u0129nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Ante Rebic, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Rebic \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Eintracht Frankfurt \u1edf \u0110\u1ee9c, v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Arsenal c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M.U h\u1ecfi mua 2 ng\u00f4i sao Croatia Rebic v\u00e0 Rakitic\" title=\"Rebic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/mu-chi-92-trieu-bang-cho-bo-doi-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U h\u1ecfi mua 2 ng\u00f4i sao Croatia Rebic v\u00e0 Rakitic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u0103m nay, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 3 t\u00e2n binh l\u00e0 Fred, Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Lee Grant. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Mourinho v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa, bao g\u1ed3m 1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p chia tay Anthony Martial, M.U s\u1ebd \u0111em v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham, Wilian, Gareth Bale &ndash; v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 M.U h\u1ecfi mua 2 ng\u00f4i sao Croatia Ivan Perisic c\u00f9ng Ante Rebic.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 Fabinho, Keita, Shaqiri; Man City c\u00f3 Riyad Mahrez; Arsenal s\u1edf h\u1eefu 5 t\u00e2n binh v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t &ndash; Chelsea c\u0169ng k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Jorginho. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung n\u00e0y d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-duoc-khuyen-nen-trao-bang-doi-truong-cho-pogba-172-191419.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/DT-Phap-tao-dang-cung-cup-vang-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-duoc-khuyen-nen-trao-bang-doi-truong-cho-pogba-172-191419.html\">Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean trao b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Pogba</span><br>\r\nTheo m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i b\u00e1o tr\u00ean The Sun, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng Pogba l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-1707-172-191425.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/1/12/tong-hop-nhung-sieu-pham-ban-thang-cua-ronaldo-khi-con-o-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-1707-172-191425.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 17/07</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i \u1edf, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 17/07.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1343","checkdouble":"191418"},{"date":"11:00 17/07","title":"Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean trao b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/DT-Phap-tao-dang-cung-cup-vang-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i b\u00e1o tr\u00ean The Sun, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng Pogba l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.\r\n</h2><h2><br />\r\nPogba n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem x\u00e9t l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0i b\u00e1o n\u00e0y ph\u00e2n t\u00edch, Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u1eeba qua, g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbp gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. V\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 Hugo Lloris \u0111ang n\u1eafm chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, nh\u01b0ng Pogba v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Les Bleus.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong bu\u1ed5i vinh danh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, \u0111\u1ee9ng ra ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eeda tri\u1ec7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p. V\u00e0 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a M.U l\u00e0 Michael Carrick gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7, nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n David De Gea hay Nemanja Matic ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, Paul Pogba ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1edbt m\u00e0u m\u00e8 v\u00e0 t\u00f4 v\u1ebd h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, anh ti\u1ebft ch\u1ebf h\u01a1n, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tham gia nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt khi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. Trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tung ra \u0111\u00fang 2 c\u00fa s\u00fat trong b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-1, tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ham &ldquo;s\u00fat b\u1eady&rdquo; trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man United.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U\" title=\"Paul Pogba t\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng v\u1edbi t\u01b0 th\u1ebf quen thu\u1ed9c.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/DT-Phap-tao-dang-cung-cup-vang-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br />\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7 Rami chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n r\u1eb1ng, Pogba \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t chi\u00eau, nh\u01b0ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ecf h\u00e1ng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 m\u1ed5 h\u00f4i, x\u1eafn tay \u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh. K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t.&rdquo;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p &ndash; Hugo Lloris c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng, Pogba \u0111ang d\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, The Sun kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, Mourinho th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 n\u00ean suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd k\u00edch th\u00edch tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 gia t\u0103ng s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng gi\u1eefa 2 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/cau-chuyen-xuc-dong-ve-tam-op-chan-cua-pogba-tai-world-cup-2018-188-191415.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/cau-chuyen-xuc-dong-ve-tam-op-chan-cua-pogba-tai-world-cup-2018.jpeg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/cau-chuyen-xuc-dong-ve-tam-op-chan-cua-pogba-tai-world-cup-2018-188-191415.html\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pogba t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span><br />\r\nTrong su\u1ed1t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Paul Pogba lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef trong tay t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n, n\u01a1i in h\u00ecnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ed1 y\u00eau d\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a anh qua \u0111\u1eddi c\u00e1ch...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cac-huyen-thoai-mu-ca-ngoi-pogba-cho-phep-doi-kieu-toc-421-191349.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/cac-huyen-thoai-mu-ca-ngoi-pogba-cho-phep-doi-kieu-toc.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cac-huyen-thoai-mu-ca-ngoi-pogba-cho-phep-doi-kieu-toc-421-191349.html\">C\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba, cho ph\u00e9p... \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c</span><br />\r\nNh\u1eefng Rio Ferdinand, Paul Scholes hay kh\u00f3 t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 Roy Keane cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1edf m\u00e0y n\u1edf m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf sau khi c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-len-ngoi-vo-dich-pogba-va-man-trinh-dien-dap-tan-moi-chi-trich-421-191329.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/pogba-duoc-huyen-thoai-khen-ngoi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-len-ngoi-vo-dich-pogba-va-man-trinh-dien-dap-tan-moi-chi-trich-421-191329.html\">Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch: Paul Pogba v\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1eadp tan m\u1ecdi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</span><br />\r\n0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng Pogba trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1342","checkdouble":"191419"},{"date":"10:40 17/07","title":"C\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n t\u1eebng gi\u00fap Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u1ecb thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/20/cong-than-tung-giup-quang-nam-vo-dich-bi-thanh-ly-hop-dong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Claudecir Junior do g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i</h2><h2>CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Claudecir</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Claudecir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Claudecir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/5/CLB-Quang-Nam-thanh-ly-hop-dong-voi-Claudecir-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Claudecir \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Claudecir Junior l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u1ea1i V-League 2017, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 23 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean t\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Claudecir \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i do ch\u1ecbu \u00e1n k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt t\u1eeb CLB, Claudecir \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 7 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Qu\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng 10 V-League, Claudecir c\u00f2n d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng sau pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 TP.HCM, Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0110\u00ecnh Lu\u1eadt. Theo k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u0129, Claudecir b\u1ecb g\u00e3y x\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e1c v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ea3ng Nam g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi m\u1ea5t \u0111i m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t ngo\u1ea1i binh. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0n b\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i t\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u2018\u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ai n\u1ea5y \u0111i\u2019. H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, ch\u00ednh Claudecir mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i nh\u01b0ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BL\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia tay \u2018c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n\u2019 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung t\u00e2n binh Warley Oliveira thay th\u1ebf. Ng\u00f4i sao v\u1eeba gia nh\u1eadp Qu\u1ea3ng Nam n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Brazil. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Oliveira t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i cho nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi sang ch\u00e2u \u00c1 th\u1eed s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh \u1edf\u00a0Kuwait m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra m\u1eaft\u00a0cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua tr\u01b0\u1edbc SLNA, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ghi b\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Claudecir, m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng b\u1ecb thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00e0 sao nh\u1eadp t\u1ecbch Nguy\u1ec5n Trung \u0110\u1ea1i D\u01b0\u01a1ng (Suleiman). Thay th\u1ebf anh l\u00e0 Thiago, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eafp ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadp t\u1ecbch v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ea1i L\u1ed9c<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 hai su\u1ea5t ngo\u1ea1i binh l\u00e0 Douglas, Warley Oliveira c\u00f9ng su\u1ea5t nh\u1eadp t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i L\u1ed9c (Thiago). Qu\u1ea3ng Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 9 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 23 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng khi k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1edbi 25 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 19 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191249.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-quang-nam-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191249.html\">SLNA 2-1 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam (KT): Thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ee9 7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Th\u1eafng v\u00e0 Olaha, SLNA \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC, qua \u0111\u00f3 n\u00e2ng chu\u1ed7i to\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-quang-nam-44-binh-duong-vong-18-vleague-2018-325-190702.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/tong-hop-quang-nam-44-binh-duong-vong-18-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-quang-nam-44-binh-duong-vong-18-vleague-2018-325-190702.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 4-4 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng (V\u00f2ng 18 V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nHai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3. Trong \u0111\u00f3, \u0110inh Thanh Trung c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0 Ti\u1ebfn Linh c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam-168-190172.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam-168-190172.html\">HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u00f9 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1341","checkdouble":"191420"},{"date":"11:25 17/07","title":"M.U chi 92 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/mu-chi-92-trieu-bang-cho-bo-doi-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, HLV Mourinho \u0111ang thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c BL\u0110 M.U h\u1ecfi mua 2 ng\u00f4i sao Croatia c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U chi g\u1ea7n 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Ivan Perisic, c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u1ecd t\u1eebng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Inter \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, khi anh g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3, ng\u00f4i sao Croatia c\u0169ng ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Anh trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. T\u1eeb l\u00e2u, Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 48 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Perisic v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, v\u00e0 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Man United.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp theo, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng \u0111ang theo s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u0129nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Ante Rebic, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Rebic \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Eintracht Frankfurt \u1edf \u0110\u1ee9c, v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Arsenal c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M.U h\u1ecfi mua 2 ng\u00f4i sao Croatia Rebic v\u00e0 Rakitic\" title=\"Rebic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/mu-chi-92-trieu-bang-cho-bo-doi-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U h\u1ecfi mua 2 ng\u00f4i sao Croatia Rebic v\u00e0 Rakitic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u0103m nay, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 3 t\u00e2n binh l\u00e0 Fred, Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Lee Grant. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Mourinho v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa, bao g\u1ed3m 1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p chia tay Anthony Martial, M.U s\u1ebd \u0111em v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham, Wilian, Gareth Bale &ndash; v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 M.U h\u1ecfi mua 2 ng\u00f4i sao Croatia Ivan Perisic c\u00f9ng Ante Rebic.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 Fabinho, Keita, Shaqiri; Man City c\u00f3 Riyad Mahrez; Arsenal s\u1edf h\u1eefu 5 t\u00e2n binh v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t &ndash; Chelsea c\u0169ng k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Jorginho. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung n\u00e0y d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-duoc-khuyen-nen-trao-bang-doi-truong-cho-pogba-172-191419.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/DT-Phap-tao-dang-cung-cup-vang-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-duoc-khuyen-nen-trao-bang-doi-truong-cho-pogba-172-191419.html\">Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean trao b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Pogba</span><br>\r\nTheo m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i b\u00e1o tr\u00ean The Sun, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng Pogba l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-1707-172-191425.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/1/12/tong-hop-nhung-sieu-pham-ban-thang-cua-ronaldo-khi-con-o-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-1707-172-191425.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 17/07</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i \u1edf, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 17/07.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1340","checkdouble":"191421"},{"date":"11:29 17/07","title":"Giroud vui m\u1eebng sau khi l\u00e0m c\u00e2m l\u1eb7ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/giroud-vui-mung-sau-khi-lam-cam-lang-nhung-loi-chi-trich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Giroud kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t sung s\u01b0\u1edbng sau khi l\u00e0m c\u00e2m l\u1eb7ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u0103ng quang \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>Giroud ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng quang v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-2 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia t\u1ea1i Luzhniki. Antoine Griezmann v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u1ef1u binh Olivier Giroud.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Giroud kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, anh c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tung ra m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u00fat tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 31 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng cao danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Ph\u00e1p. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Giroud.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Giroud vui m\u1eebng sau khi c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u0103ng quang \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Giroud vui m\u1eebng sau khi c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u0103ng quang \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/giroud-vui-mung-sau-khi-lam-cam-lang-nhung-loi-chi-trich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Giroud vui m\u1eebng sau khi \u0111\u0103ng quang World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 \u2018b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0\u2019\u201d, Giroud ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u k\u00e8m m\u1ed9t n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u00fa th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t c\u1ea3m k\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f4i khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vinh d\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd cho t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Giroud h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho r\u1eb1ng Giroud c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t quan tr\u1ecdng trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Les Bleus n\u0103m nay nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 si\u00eang n\u0103ng v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u1edf Ph\u00e1p. V\u00ed d\u1ee5 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 khi t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf World Cup, t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p t\u1eeb c\u00e1c C\u0110V v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chuy\u00ean gia. H\u1ecd nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 t\u00f4i l\u00e0m cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ghi b\u00e0n. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n \u01b0u ti\u00ean l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u00edch cho t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i c\u0169ng th\u1ebf. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 1, 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi hay 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p n\u0103m nay\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T\u00a0Ph\u00e1p:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-vo-dich-world-cup-nhung-se-khong-the-thong-tri-the-gioi-421-191391.html\">Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/vo-dich-world-cup-2018-phap-duoc-nhan-bao-nhieu-tien-tu-fifa-465-191336.html\">V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n t\u1eeb FIFA?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1339","checkdouble":"191423"},{"date":"11:16 17/07","title":"Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo: Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/juventus-chieu-mo-ronaldo-khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u nghi ng\u1edd v\u00e0 th\u1eafc m\u1eafc xung quanh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e1m b\u1ecf t\u1edbi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro ch\u1ec9 cho m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao, tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng hoan ngh\u00eanh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi k\u00e9o d\u00e0i v\u00f4 t\u1eadn</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGhi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i Champions League \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u00f3i quen nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n, trong \u0111\u00eam Turin \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 4 v\u1eeba qua, <em>si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Juventus</em>. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00fa &ldquo;xe \u0111\u1ea1p ch\u1ed5ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c&rdquo; th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a anh <u>nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00e1n th\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh c\u00e1c C\u0110V t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Allianz</u>. Trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Juventus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Juventus-chieu-mo-Ronaldo-Khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Juventus h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 4</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Bianconeri s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc phi th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nhen nh\u00f3m trong \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u s\u00e2n Allianz. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i, 3 th\u00e1ng sau, h\u1ecd <strong>bi\u1ebfn m\u01a1 th\u00e0nh th\u1ef1c v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro</strong>. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean cho th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi khi b\u1ecf s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CLB v\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia. \u0110\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i, <em>h\u1ecd c\u00f3 Ronaldo &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh 5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League</em> v\u00e0 5 Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Juventus-chieu-mo-Ronaldo-Khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo gi\u00e0nh v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 danh hi\u1ec7u trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Juventus, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 CLB n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ronaldo h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 khi <u>c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi m\u1edf ra, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Juve kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1</u>. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t cho nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus-176-191385.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bianconeri c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y</span> t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t ph\u00e9p t\u00ednh: Ronaldo 33 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro? Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, <em>nh\u1eefng nghi v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo \u0111ang k\u00e9o d\u00e0i t\u1edbi v\u00f4 t\u1eadn</em>. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00e0o l\u00e0 Juventus c\u00f3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u00f4ng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u? Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n Ronaldo? Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n? Ronaldo c\u00f3 c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9?&nbsp; Ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Juventus s\u1ebd ngh\u0129 sao? Juventus c\u00f3 l\u00e2m v\u00e0o ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n? C\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ec1n l\u1ec7 x\u1ea5u cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia? v.v. v\u00e0 v.v.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo roi Real mang theo nhieu danh hieu\" title=\"Ronaldo roi Real mang theo nhieu danh hieu\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Ronaldo-roi-Real-mang-theo-nhieu-danh-hieu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">CR7 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c chinh ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nKhi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn: Cho t\u1edbi <u>tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi r\u1eddi Real, Ronaldo v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 1</u> c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. 44 b\u00e0n sau 44 tr\u1eadn v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i. T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u01a1i r\u1ed9ng, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00ecnh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t &ldquo;s\u00e1t th\u1ee7&rdquo; v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 33.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng <em>Serie A l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u1ec7t ng\u00e3 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng</em>. Nh\u1eefng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Francesco Totti v\u00e0 Javier Zanetti c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t cho t\u1edbi tu\u1ed5i 40. Ch\u1eb3ng n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2u xa, Fabio Quagliarella d\u00f9 35 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 4 trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Serie A m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi 19 b\u00e0n sau 35 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus chieu mo Ronaldo\" title=\"Juventus chieu mo Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/juventus-chieu-mo-ronaldo-khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 l\u00fd khi Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng lo ng\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 t\u1eebng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n khi Juventus th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; 90 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u1edbi Gonzalo Higuain c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m. Khi \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 28 tu\u1ed5i. Nh\u01b0ng con s\u1ed1 55 b\u00e0n sau 105 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0 Higuain ghi cho Juve t\u1edbi nay l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i ch\u00fat n\u00e0o (trung b\u00ecnh 0,52 b\u00e0n/ tr\u1eadn).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Juventus s\u1ebd c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 Ronaldo, Higuain, Dybala v\u00e0 Douglas Costa khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i n\u1ec3 s\u1ee3. N\u1ebfu ai \u0111\u00f3 lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Bianconeri m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, xin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Joao Cancelo v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Emre Can.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus s\u1edbm m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 song s\u00e1t t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Higuain</span><br>\r\n<span>C\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y: Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro,...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 g\u00f3i g\u1ecdn tham v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Serie A, Juventus c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; v\u1edbi Ronaldo. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i n\u00e0y 7 n\u0103m qua v\u00e0 d\u00f9 \u00edt d\u00f9 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m&rdquo; ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 an nh\u00e0n m\u1ed7i n\u0103m n\u00e2ng cao Scudetto v\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f4i khi bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh. <strong>Juventus mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i vinh quang t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</strong>, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 12 n\u0103m. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2 l\u1ea7n trong 4 m\u00f9a qua nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 Barcelona v\u00e0 Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tong hop: Inter Milan 2-3 Juventus (Vong 35 Serie A 2017/18)\" title=\"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Inter Milan 2-3 Juventus (V\u00f2ng 35 Serie A 2017/18)\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/29/tong-hop-inter-milan-23-juventus-vong-35-serie-a-201718.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Juventus \u0111ang m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 Champions League sau 12 n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft b\u1edfi ch\u00ednh Real v\u00e0 b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi t\u1eeb penalty ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 do ch\u00ednh Ronaldo th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n. C\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea1i Champions League, Juve ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb CR7 l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 10 l\u1ea7n sau 7 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ea5y v\u1ec1 th\u1ee9 v\u0169 kh\u00ed l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng vua \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m Real Madrid, l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 l\u00e0 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ed3i. Real \u0111\u00e3 3 n\u0103m li\u1ec1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League (4 l\u1ea7n sau 5 n\u0103m) v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo &ndash; ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 1 coi nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tri\u1ec7t ti\u00eau s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo toi Juventus\" title=\"Ronaldo toi Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Ronaldo-toi-Juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Allianz</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Juventus mang v\u1ec1 Ronaldo c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 khi PSG ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 222 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u1edbi Neymar. T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n m\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil mang l\u1ea1i cho PSG th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus th\u1ea5y r\u00f5. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf phi\u1ebfu cao \u0111\u1ec3 CLB m\u1edf k\u00e9t tr\u1ea3 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay t\u1eeb l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/juventus-ban-520-nghin-ao-dau-du-cristiano-ronaldo-con-chua-ra-mat-465-191382.html\" target=\"_blank\">l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n ra c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t</span> v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec m\u1ed9t b\u00e1u v\u1eadt t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh Turin. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u1eb1m trong t\u00ednh to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Juventus, h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng sau 4 n\u0103m, CR7 th\u00f4ng qua th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rat nhieu CDV Juventus chao don su xuat hien cua Ronaldo.\" title=\"R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V Juventus ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/FBL-ITA-SERIEA-JUVENTUS-RONALDO-(2).jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u0110V Juventus nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a CR7</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ef1c b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd: Tr\u00ean th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Juventus n\u0103m qua v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 doanh thu b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Inter Milan b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i. S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1n c\u00e2n n\u00e0y thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ed5 phi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Juve \u0111ang t\u0103ng l\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng v\u00e0 &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m&rdquo; d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u0169ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hoan ngh\u00eanh, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee9 r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 (c\u00fap b\u1ea1c Champions League), vi\u1ec7c Juve l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng l\u00e0m (mua m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro) c\u0169ng l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-tiet-lo-soc-ve-vu-chuyen-nhuong-toi-juventus-184-191410.html\">Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-real-noi-gi-khi-ronaldo-toi-juventus-180-191404.html\">HLV Real n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mourinho-ronaldo-se-phuc-hung-bong-da-y-176-191396.html\">Mourinho: &ldquo;Ronaldo s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5c h\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/hanh-dong-thu-vi-cua-ronaldo-khi-gioi-thieu-ao-dau-tai-juventus-327-191392.html\">H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00fa v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Ronaldo khi gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/sao-juventus-noi-gi-ve-dong-doi-tan-binh-ronaldo-176-191387.html\">Sao Juventus n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u00e2n binh Ronaldo?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus-176-191385.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Juventus, Cristiano Ronaldo n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1338","checkdouble":"191424"},{"date":"11:12 17/07","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 17/07","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/1/12/tong-hop-nhung-sieu-pham-ban-thang-cua-ronaldo-khi-con-o-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i \u1edf, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 17/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU chi 92 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 1707 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 1707 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-1707-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Perisic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Express, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 92 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Ivan Perisic v\u00e0 Ante Rebic c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 62\u00a0tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Perisic v\u00e0 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Rebic. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Man \u0111\u1ecf nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Perisic nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb Inter Milan t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Daley Blind tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ajax</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-utd-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-cau-thu-tiep-theo-sau-4-nam-gan-bo-172-191388.html\" target=\"_blank\">Daley Blind \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ajax</span> v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 14 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Anh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ajax.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-utd-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-cau-thu-tiep-theo-sau-4-nam-gan-bo-172-191388.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/15/man-utd-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-cau-thu-tiep-theo-sau-4-nam-gan-bo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-utd-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-cau-thu-tiep-theo-sau-4-nam-gan-bo-172-191388.html\">Man Utd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo sau 4 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3</span><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Daley Blind \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn r\u1eddi Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng Ajax Amsterdam trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern nh\u1eafm Martial thay Arjen Robben</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bayern Munich \u0111ang nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a M.U thay th\u1ebf Arjen Robben, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Luke Shaw mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford n\u1ebfu...</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Co y thuc cuu van tuong lai ban than, Luke Shaw la cau thu hiem hoi choi tot trong tran MU hoa West Ham\" title=\"C\u00f3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, Luke Shaw l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ebfm hoi ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong tr\u00e2n MU h\u00f2a West Ham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/11/101753-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luke Shaw c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi MU n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Luke Shaw kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd r\u1eddi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi Young.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U ch\u1ec9 nh\u1ea3 Lukaku cho Real n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 Gareth Bale</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Don Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real nh\u1eafm Romelu Lukaku thay Ronaldo, song Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 cho Los Blancos n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 Gareth Bale theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU kh\u00f4ng h\u1ecfi mua Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Real Madrid c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, song Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3. Mourinho kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho nh\u1eafm Bonucci n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo The Sun, HLV Jose Mourinho mu\u1ed1n M.U mua trung v\u1ec7 Bonucci c\u1ee7a AC Milan \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 tin c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Eric Bailly h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 th\u00e9p tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a David de Gea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Danny Rose</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danny Rose Mauricio Pochettino\" title=\"Danny Rose Mauricio Pochettino\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/21/Danny-Rose-chi-trich-Tottenham,-chac-chan-ra-di-he-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Rose</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Danny Rose c\u1ee7a Tottenham, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chi 115 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Martial</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a MU trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Eden Hazard t\u1edbi Real Madrid, The Blues c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 115 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chi-115-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-hazard-172-191418.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/chelsea-chi-115-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-hazard.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chi-115-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-hazard-172-191418.html\">Chelsea chi 115 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Hazard</span><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a MU trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Eden Hazard t\u1edbi Real Madrid, The Blues c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 115 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1337","checkdouble":"191425"},{"date":"11:48 17/07","title":"X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00e1n t\u00f9 d\u00e0nh cho 4 C\u0110V ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/17/xac-dinh-an-tu-danh-cho-4-cdv-chay-vao-san-tran-chung-ket-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia v\u1eeba qua, m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m 4 C\u0110V ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft trong hi\u1ec7p 2, khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ecb gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n \u00edt ph\u00fat.\r\n</h2><h2>Pussy Riot l\u00e0 ai?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng C\u0110V b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, m\u00e0 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a nh\u00f3m Pussy Riot &ndash; m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Nga ch\u1ed1ng ph\u00e1 Putin. 4 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean bi\u1ec3u t\u00ecnh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1m tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u00f3m g\u1ecdn ch\u1ec9 sau 1 ph\u00fat b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n l\u00ean m\u1eb7t c\u1ecf SV\u0110 Luzhniki.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quay l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, 4 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0103n v\u1eadn nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Nga, m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eadp tay v\u1edbi sao tr\u1ebb Kylian Mbappe. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng an ninh t\u1ea1i SV\u0110 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng r\u1ea5t nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 gi\u00fap tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pussy Riot\" title=\"Pussy Riot\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/xac-dinh-an-tu-danh-cho-4-cdv-chay-vao-san-tran-chung-ket-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m 4 C\u0110V ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Pussy Riot \u0111\u00e3 k\u00eau g\u1ecdi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga ph\u00f3ng th\u00edch t\u00f9 nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb, ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t c\u00e1c v\u1ee5 b\u1eaft gi\u1eef b\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p trong c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c bi\u1ec3u t\u00ecnh. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd y\u00eau c\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, khi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c n\u00e0y m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t t\u1ed1ng giam v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n t\u00f9. Theo \u0111\u00f3, 4 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean n\u00e0y s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ng\u1ed3i kh\u00e1m trong 15 ng\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u1ea5m tham d\u1ef1 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u00e1c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 thao trong v\u00f2ng 3 n\u0103m t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pussy Riot n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c bi\u1ec3u t\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 th\u1edd Moscow v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2012, trong \u0111\u00f3 3 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tha v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u1ed1ng ph\u00e1. \u0110\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2014, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb giam gi\u1eef 1 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1eddi \u0111e d\u1ecda s\u1ebd l\u00e0m lo\u1ea1n tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pussy Riot\" title=\"Pussy Riot\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/a.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Pussy Riot \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb k\u1ebft \u00e1n ng\u1ed3i t\u00f9 15 ng\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cac-cdv-chay-vao-san-trong-tran-chung-ket-phap-vs-croatia-la-ai-421-191307.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/cac-cdv-chay-vao-san-trong-tran-chung-ket-phap-vs-croatia-la-ai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cac-cdv-chay-vao-san-trong-tran-chung-ket-phap-vs-croatia-la-ai-421-191307.html\">C\u00e1c C\u0110V ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia l\u00e0 ai?</span><br>\r\nTrong hi\u1ec7p 2 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ecb gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n \u00edt ph\u00fat.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1336","checkdouble":"191427"},{"date":"07:23 17/07","title":"T\u00e2n HLV Sarri: \u201cV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 cho t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 5-6 Chelsea \u1edf Anh\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/tan-hlv-sarri-van-de-cho-toi-la-co-den-56-chelsea-o-anh.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean gh\u00e9 n\u00f3ng Stamford Bridge.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chia \u0111\u00f4i con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi Antonio Conte sau hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1eafn b\u00f3 mang v\u1ec1 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u00e0 FA Cup, Chelsea nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd kh\u00e1c v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u00e2n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a CLB. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng Maurizio Sarri</span> sau nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u1edf Napoli gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/chelsea-sap-chao-don-4-tan-binh-duoi-thoi-sarri.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2n HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Sarri nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 59 tu\u1ed5i trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean xu\u1ea5t ngo\u1ea1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Anh. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Sarri c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 chia s\u1ebb l\u00fd do:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cChelsea l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh, nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 cho t\u00f4i l\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 5-6 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e9m g\u00ec Chelsea, trong khi t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u00edt s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh h\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u00e0y \u1edf \u00dd.\u201d \u2013 Sarri nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh nh\u00f3m Big Six kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t, trong khi \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Juventus hay c\u00f9ng l\u1eafm Roma \u1edf qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng tri\u1ebft l\u00fd v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o Chelsea m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch h\u1ee3p l\u00fd nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nhau v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh l\u00e0m. Tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 may m\u1eafn v\u00e0 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u1edf Napoli v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng Chelsea c\u0169ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.\u201d \u2013 Sarri s\u1ebd ra m\u1eaft Chelsea \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean IC Cup g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Inter Milan, Arsenal v\u00e0 Lyon. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Man City.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/_102527296_jorginho_getty2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span><br>\r\nChelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge t\u1eeb Napoli v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1335","checkdouble":"191394"},{"date":"07:54 17/07","title":"Mourinho: \u201cRonaldo s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5c h\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/mourinho-ronaldo-se-phuc-hung-bong-da-y.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ee7a Man Utd ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Serie A sau khi Juventus n\u1ed5 qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y: Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 vinh quang \u1edf Bernabeu nh\u1eb1m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi \u1edf m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd khi \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/hanh-dong-thu-vi-cua-ronaldo-khi-gioi-thieu-ao-dau-tai-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real sang Juventus, v\u1edbi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh xung quanh vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd khi Serie A gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Theo \u0111\u00f3, HLV c\u1ee7a Man Utd cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n ph\u1ee5c h\u01b0ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng phanh trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1eb7c Bi\u1ec7t: \u201cLa Liga \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n s\u1edf h\u1eefu hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf Italia. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u00f3 Premier League, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n c\u1ea3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady n\u00ean gi\u1edd ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ch\u00e2n ki\u1ec1ng c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u1edf Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, khi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 xem La Liga v\u00ec c\u00f3 Messi, xem Serie A v\u00ec c\u00f3 Ronaldo v\u00e0 xem Premier League v\u00ec n\u00f3 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t h\u00e0nh tinh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m v\u1ecb th\u1ebf, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng cho Juventus, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n ph\u1ee5c h\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd, t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh. Ngh\u0129 m\u00e0 xem nh\u1eefng Roma, Napoli, AC Milan v\u00e0 Inter Milan s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 \u00fd th\u1ee9c m\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb t\u1ee5t l\u1ea1i ph\u00eda sau so v\u1edbi Juve.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus-176-191385.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus-176-191385.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Juventus, Cristiano Ronaldo n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o ra m\u1eaft Juventus v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1334","checkdouble":"191396"},{"date":"08:49 17/07","title":"Ivan Perisic n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi t\u1edbi M.U c\u1ee7a Mourinho?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/ivan-perisic-noi-gi-truoc-loi-moi-goi-toi-mu-cua-mourinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi HLV Mourinho l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Perisic, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Ivan Perisic \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a Mourinho</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ivan Perisic n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi t\u1edbi MU c\u1ee7a Mourinho  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ivan Perisic n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi t\u1edbi MU c\u1ee7a Mourinho  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/2/Ivan-Perisic-noi-gi-truoc-loi-moi-goi-toi-MU-cua-Mourinho--hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Perisic ch\u01b0a quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gia nh\u1eadp Man United</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Perisic l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB Man United theo \u0111u\u1ed5i trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 2017, tuy nhi\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra sau khi c\u00e1c b\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 n\u0103m nay, M.U \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Perisic sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Ngay c\u1ea3 HLV Mourinho c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u tham v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 Old Trafford.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao Perisic l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng gia nh\u1eadp Man United khi t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d, Mourinho tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a Mourinho, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Perisic c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng. Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Croatia m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup\u00a02018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft: \"Chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Man United \u00e0? L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00e2m tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 d\u00e0nh cho Croatia. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. Sau \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung cho CLB Inter Milan\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Perisic c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh cho th\u1ea5y anh d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay Inter. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Nerazzurri c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi th\u00e1ng 6/2022.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-chi-ra-mu-can-chieu-mo-ngay-sao-bu-dt-croatia-421-191381.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/2/Ivan-Perisic-noi-gi-truoc-loi-moi-goi-toi-MU-cua-Mourinho--hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-chi-ra-mu-can-chieu-mo-ngay-sao-bu-dt-croatia-421-191381.html\">3 l\u00fd do ch\u1ec9 ra M.U c\u1ea7n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ngay sao b\u1ef1 \u0110T Croatia</span><br>\r\nIvan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Croatia. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do cho th\u1ea5y M.U c\u1ea7n mua g\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Inter Milan trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-1507-mu-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-khung-nguoi-italia-184-191267.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/17/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-1507-mu-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-khung-nguoi-italia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-1507-mu-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-khung-nguoi-italia-184-191267.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 15/07: MU chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 15/07.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1333","checkdouble":"191400"},{"date":"08:40 17/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 17/7: Ronaldo v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh b\u00e1o h\u1ea1i Man Utd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/14/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-177-ronaldo-vo-tinh-bao-hai-man-utd.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 17/7.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n Ronaldo, Real quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Bale</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24hvn s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 177 - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24hvn s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 177 - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/ngay-hom-nay-gareth-bale-xac-dinh-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Gareth Bale</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y m\u1edbi n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng CR7 \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh b\u00e1o h\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Man Utd v\u1ed1n tham v\u1ecdng nghi\u00eam t\u00fac chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi X\u1ee9 Wales v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u1ebfu Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chia tay m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c sang Juventus. V\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do m\u00e0 Gareth Bale v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Julen Lopetegui.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City b\u1ecb Real Madrid h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp v\u1ee5 sao Croatia<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 177 Ronaldo v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh b\u00e1o h\u1ea1i Man Utd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 177 Ronaldo v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh b\u00e1o h\u1ea1i Man Utd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/2/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-177-Ronaldo-vo-tinh-bao-hai-Man-Utd-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Mateo Kovacic</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u1eeb Fred sang Man Utd \u0111\u1ebfn Jorginho sang Man City, HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e0nh l\u00f2ng chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic nh\u1eb1m gia c\u1ed1 tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao Croatia v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy ho\u1ea1ch d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n \u1edf Bernabeu n\u00ean ch\u1eb3ng t\u1ed9i g\u00ec Real Madrid ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n anh, ti\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u00e9o \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man Utd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay Daley Blind<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Daley Blind\" title=\"Daley Blind\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/15/man-utd-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-cau-thu-tiep-theo-sau-4-nam-gan-bo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Daley Blind</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jose Mourinho tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Old Trafford, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan n\u1eafm l\u1ea5y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p ngay trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Ajax Amsterdam. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Man Utd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn b\u00e1n l\u1ea1i Daley Blind cho \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 14 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00eam 5 tri\u1ec7u t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lyon ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u1ed1i l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Fekir\" title=\"tien ve Fekir\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/liverpool-khong-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-fekir.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nabil Fekir</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh Lyon c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1eaft \u0111\u1ee9t \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1ed1n \u0111ang su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho Liverpool v\u00ec l\u00fd do m\u1eb7c c\u1ea3 l\u1eb1ng nh\u1eb1ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Nabil Fekir. Gi\u1edd sau khi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Jean Michael Aulas l\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 hai cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00f9ng Merseyside trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea t\u00ednh cu\u1ed7m Higuain kh\u1ecfi Juventus<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gonzalo Higuain cua Juventus\" title=\"Gonzalo Higuain cua Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/23/chelsea-sap-co-tien-dao-tri-gia-53-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Gonzalo Higuain</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mang th\u00eam c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u00ean \u00dd v\u1ec1 Anh \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ebf ch\u1ebf m\u1edbi \u1edf Stamford Bridge. Chelsea v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Gonzalo Higuain t\u1eeb l\u00e2u v\u00e0 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Juventus \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Cristiano Ronaldo, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3. El Pipita \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool v\u00e0 Chelsea mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng hot World Cup 2018<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alex Golovin\" title=\"Alex Golovin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/hang-hot-tuyen-nga-tiep-tuc-ban-tin-hieu-cho-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Aleksandr Golovin</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi Liverpool t\u0103m tia Domagoj Vida, trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111o\u1ea1t ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a Croatia, \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p c\u1eb7p b\u00e0i tr\u00f9ng \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi Dejan Lovren \u1edf Anfield, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng duy\u1ec7t chi 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00ec Aleksandr Golovin. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Monaco l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang t\u00ednh nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o ph\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1m trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec3n trai ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga m\u1edbi 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Atletico Madrid s\u1eafp c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb gh\u00e9t nh\u1ea5t Croatia<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kalinic bi duoi co ve nuoc\" title=\"Kalinic b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ed1 v\u1ec3 n\u01b0\u1edbc\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/hoc-tay-ban-nha-croatia-duoi-nguoi-ngay-thoi-diem-dien-ra-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nikola Kalinic</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">HLV Diego Simeone mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng sau khi chia tay Fernando Torres. C\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng ng\u1eafm ngh\u00eda l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Nikola Kalinic, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 30 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecb t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Croatia \u1edf World Cup 2018 can t\u1ed9i\u2026 ch\u1ea3nh. Nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00e0y hi\u1ec7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o AC Milan nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m tham d\u1ef1 c\u00e1c c\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u trong v\u00f2ng hai n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1332","checkdouble":"191403"},{"date":"23:17 16/07","title":"\u0110T Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed9 t\u1ed1ng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e1y bay chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u trong ng\u00e0y tr\u1edf v\u1ec1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/4E4E727900000578-0-image-m-44_1531738533364.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018, \u0110T Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed9 t\u1ed1ng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e1y bay chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u trong ng\u00e0y tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc.\r\nN.D (TTVN)\r\n</h2><div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cac cau thu DT Croatia ve nuoc sau khi gianh ngoi a quan World Cup 2018.\" title=\"C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110T Croatia v\u1ec1 n\u